I had an incredible time on planet Burning Man & took my time editing & reliving the experience. This year was one of my favorites... I got to witnessing Burning Man through a new lens🙌🏽 Tag 3 friends you would go to Burning Man with. 
tawnyjanae

node.text: Few days ago I spoke on my anxiety and mental health. I want to thank you all that have reached out. I was a little nervous to get that vulnerable with everyone that follows me. But what I realized is we should be doing this. Especially people with large following. Large influencers just put out beautiful lives, flexing with Material things, etc. Also I’ve done this. I think it’s good sometimes to be relatable we need to let people know that they’re not alone and help educate. So that being said whenever I need to move my anxiety I like to work out at the gym. what some of yours? 📸 @juditmoreno22

node.text: Just found the love of my life!! Her name is Sabina I’m a call her Bean.  She is up for adoption! 6 year old Doberman been thru it. I’m taking her!!!!!❤️ 📷 @amirimage

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jesse Wellens on May 09, 2021. May be an image of 4 people and people standing.

node.text: Mother’s Day❤️ please tell your Mom how much you love her..spend some time with her. I lost my mom 5 years ago and to this day my heart hurts. I miss her so much. She was the fu*king coolest! She really did start the trend carrying her dog around in a purse lol..she was so caring for everyone else over her self. She would bring people off the streets that were homeless and let them live in her house!! She just really taught me how to be caring for everyone no matter what. I do thank my mom for tuning me into who I am today.  I hope I am making you proud up there Mom. ❤️ Happy Mothers Day... and I know you love being on my social media you always asked me to post you. 😊
